{"word":"G946 - βδέλυγμα - bdélygma - bdel'-oog-mah - Abomination","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">βδέλυγμα</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>bdélygma"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>bdel'-oog-mah"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Abomination"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"அருவருப்பு - பால்வேறுபாடற்ற பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"a foul thing, a detestable thing, the desolating abomination"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Neuter / பெயர்ச்சொல் (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G948 - βδελύσσω - bdelýssō - bdel-oos'-so/948\">G948</a>; a <i>detestation</i>, that is, (specifically) <i>idolatry:</i> - abomination."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G946 - βδέλυγμα - bdélygma - bdel'-oog-mah/946\">G946</a>, <a href=\"#/G947 - βδελυκτός - bdelyktós - bdel-ook-tos'/947\">G947</a>, <a href=\"#/G948 - βδελύσσω - bdelýssō - bdel-oos'-so/948\">G948</a>"}]}